        <article class="legalP" id="paragraf-5-ledd-1">F&#xF8;lgende halvautomatiske rifler som oppfyller kravene til minimum totallengde og l&#xF8;pslengde etter v&#xE5;penforskriften &#xA7; 2 f&#xF8;rste ledd, er godkjent for erverv, eie og inneha til jakt, jf. v&#xE5;penforskriften &#xA7; 7 annet ledd, dersom skytev&#xE5;penet ved fabrikk er produsert til bare &#xE5; kunne avfyre halvautomatisk ild:<ul class="defaultList"><li data-li-identifier="1." data-name="1."><article class="listArticle" id="paragraf-5-ledd-1-punkt-1"><article class="legalP" id="paragraf-5-ledd-1-punkt-1-ledd-1">Winchester M/100,</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="2." data-name="2."><article class="listArticle" id="paragraf-5-ledd-1-punkt-2"><article class="legalP" id="paragraf-5-ledd-1-punkt-2-ledd-1">Browning BAR (med unntak av Browning BAR M/1918),</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="3." data-name="3."><article class="listArticle" id="paragraf-5-ledd-1-punkt-3"><article class="legalP" id="paragraf-5-ledd-1-punkt-3-ledd-1">Remington Modell four,</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="4." data-name="4."><article class="listArticle" id="paragraf-5-ledd-1-punkt-4"><article class="legalP" id="paragraf-5-ledd-1-punkt-4-ledd-1">Remington modell 7400,</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="5." data-name="5."><article class="listArticle" id="paragraf-5-ledd-1-punkt-5"><article class="legalP" id="paragraf-5-ledd-1-punkt-5-ledd-1">Remington 742 Woodmaster,</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="6." data-name="6."><article class="listArticle" id="paragraf-5-ledd-1-punkt-6"><article class="legalP" id="paragraf-5-ledd-1-punkt-6-ledd-1">Ruger mini 14,</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="7." data-name="7."><article class="listArticle" id="paragraf-5-ledd-1-punkt-7"><article class="legalP" id="paragraf-5-ledd-1-punkt-7-ledd-1">Ruger mini 30,</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="8." data-name="8."><article class="listArticle" id="pa